clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: Celiprolol is indicated for the management of mild to moderate hypertension and effort induced angina pectoris

contraindications.disease: No data are available regarding celiprolol overdose in humans The most common symptoms to be expected following overdosage with beta adrenoceptor blocking agents are bradycardia hypotension bronchospasm and acute cardiac insufficiency
